  "texts": [
    "According to the processing method of non-overlapping point cloud, the registration method of partial overlapping point cloud based on deep learning is divided into the method for non-overlapping region, without considering the method of non-overlapping region.",
    "Point cloud data frequently can only describe the part of the object/scene that is visible to the sensor and not covered by occlusion.",
    "In addition, sensor noise, reflective surfaces, or artifacts can sometimes create points in the point cloud that do not correspond to any surface in the object or scene.",
    "Missing data and irrelevant points in point cloud pose new challenges to point cloud registration methods.",
    "The method of removing outlier pairs mentioned above cannot cope well with the registration of point clouds with low overlap rate."
  ],
